originalText.text: What a relief to find a total professional: a good communicator who does excellent quality work and is friendly and easygoing. A friend recommended Elisandro when I needed a half bath renovated and a bedroom and stairwell painted but couldn't be there in myself to oversee the work. We consulted via WhatsApp and everything flowed smoothly from there, with excellent results. I even recommended him to two neighbors in my building while he was doing my project, and both were very pleased. It's been a complete pleasure to work with this company, highly recommend!

originalText.text:
Elisandro and his team took out an old metal framed closet and opened up the closet space in my bedroom. I didn’t even know the metal frame could come out! The removal of the frame left a small hole in the floor which they patched up with another piece of wood beautifully. They also patched up the wall and painted it very nicely.
My floors are very easily scratched but Elisandro carefully put a mix of plastic, cardboard, and paper that there was not even a small scratch to be seen! He even cleaned up my floors before leaving!
I highly recommend Elisandro’s contracting business. Not only was the work professional and top notch, he and his team are friendly, trustworthy and a pleasure to work with.

originalText.text: This company was recommended to me. I am extremely grateful and blessed to have hired them. As a homeowner, I have needed to hire quite a few contractors over the years. This company is honest, professional, clean, timely,  knowledgeable, and does beautiful work. I was not on-sight while they repaired holes and stains on the walls, painted, repaired the faucet, cabinet drawers, installed a water system, made a replica of a wooden bar in the stairs rail I had broken, as well as got rid of black chalkboard paint on the wall. I cannot even see a trace of it anymore. I had no doubts recommending this company to a friend and the results are the same. 110% satisfaction,  they went above and beyond. This company is a hidden gem.

originalText.text: This company was recommended to me by one of my best friends who used them to have work done on her house. They do excellent work and are honest, trustworthy and professional. I had my entire apartment painted and new floor installed, all at a reasonable rate. The work was done in a very timely manner. Going back to them when I’m ready to have my bathroom redone.
